[2;36m                    [0m         DEDUP_TOKEN: d7514645016ef7a8                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         == libFuzzer crashing input ==                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mReport[0m===                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         # Evaluation Report                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Summary                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         A critical OS Command Injection vulnerability [1m([0mFuzzerSecurityIssueCritical[1m)[0m has     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         been detected in the Apache Tika codebase during fuzzing operations. The            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         vulnerability occurs when processing files through the ShellCodeDetector component, [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         which executes OS commands with potentially attacker-controlled data. The execution [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         path flows from TikaCLI through various parsers [1m([0mPackageParser, CompositeParser,    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         AutoDetectParser[1m)[0m before reaching the vulnerable code in [1;35mProcessUtils.execute[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         called by [1;35mShellCodeDetector.detect[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m.                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The issue is an OS Command Injection vulnerability, which represents a critical     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         security flaw where attacker-controlled data can be used to execute arbitrary       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         operating system commands, potentially leading to remote code execution.            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ### Vulnerability Details                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The vulnerability manifests through the following execution path:                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. The entry point begins at [1;35mTikaCLI.main[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m processing a file                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. The file is parsed through AutoDetectParser and CompositeParser                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. During package parsing [1m([0mPackageParser[1m)[0m, embedded documents are extracted         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m. The [1;35mFileEmbeddedDocumentExtractor.parseEmbedded[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m method is invoked              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m. A [1;35mCompositeDetector.detect[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m call triggers the [1;35mShellCodeDetector.detect[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m method [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m. ShellCodeDetector invokes [1;35mProcessUtils.execute[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m at line [1;36m94[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m. This ultimately calls [1;35mProcessBuilder.start[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m which triggers the security         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         violation                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The Jazzer sanitizer [1m([0mOsCommandInjection.processImplStartHook[1m)[0m intercepted the      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         vulnerability at [1;35mProcessBuilder.start[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m [1m([0mProcessBuilder.jav[1;92ma:1110[0m[1m)[0m, indicating that [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         the actual OS command execution was about to occur with potentially unsafe input.   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ### Key Observations                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - The vulnerability is triggered during file content detection and parsing          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         operations                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - The ShellCodeDetector component is specifically involved, suggesting it uses      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         shell commands for detection purposes                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - The vulnerable code path is reached when processing embedded documents within     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         package/archive files                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - The DEDUP_TOKEN [1m([0md7514645016ef7a8[1m)[0m indicates this is a distinct, reproducible     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         issue                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ### Areas Requiring Investigation                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         To gain a comprehensive understanding of this vulnerability, the following          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         components should be examined:                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. **ShellCodeDetector.java** [1m([0mline [1;36m103[0m[1m)[0m: Review how shell commands are constructed [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         and what data sources are used                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. **ProcessUtils.java** [1m([0mline [1;36m94[0m[1m)[0m: Examine the [1;35mexecute[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m method implementation and [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         how command arguments are handled                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. **CompositeDetector.java** [1m([0mline [1;36m84[0m[1m)[0m: Understand the detector chain and how data [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         flows to ShellCodeDetector                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m. **PackageParser.java** [1m([0mlines [1;36m481[0m, [1;36m386[0m, [1;36m336[0m, [1;36m259[0m[1m)[0m: Investigate how embedded      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         entries are extracted and processed                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m. **TikaCLI.java** [1m([0mline [1;36m1092[0m[1m)[0m: Review FileEmbeddedDocumentExtractor configuration [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         and any input sanitization                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m. The overall detector configuration and whether ShellCodeDetector can be disabled [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         or sandboxed                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The investigation should focus on identifying what user-controlled data reaches the [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         command execution point and whether proper input validation and sanitization        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         mechanisms are in place.                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Initial Issue Log                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:     * rather than discovery order. Detectors are used in the given order,[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:     * so put the Tika parsers last so that non-Tika [0m[1;39m([0m[39muser supplied[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:     * parsers can take precedence.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:     * <p>[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:     * If an [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m@link OverrideDetector[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m is loaded, it takes precedence over[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:     * all other detectors.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:     * @param loader service loader[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:     * @return ordered list of statically loadable detectors[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:    private static List<Detector> [0m[1;35mgetDefaultDetectors[0m[1;39m([0m[39mMimeTypes types, [0m          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"-b"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"--mime-type"[0m[39m,[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m123[0m[39m:                        [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mProcessUtils.escapeCommandLine[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpath.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m124[0m[39m:        ProcessBuilder builder = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39margs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m125[0m[39m:        FileProcessResult result = [0m[1;35mProcessUtils.execute[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuilder, timeoutMs, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m10000[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m10000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtika-core/src/main/resources/META-INF/services/org.apache.tika.detect.Detector:[0m[1;36m15[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m15[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m16[0m[39m:org.apache.tika.detect.ShellCodeDetector[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtika-parsers/tika-parsers-standard/tika-parsers-standard-package/src/test/resources[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m/org/apache/tika/config/TIKA-[0m[1;36m1702[0m[39m-detector-exclude.xml:[0m[1;36m21[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m26[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m21[0m[39m:  <detectors>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m22[0m[39m:    <!-- All detectors except built-in container ones -->[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m23[0m[39m:    <detector [0m[33mclass[0m[39m=[0m[32m"org[0m[32m.apache.tika.detect.DefaultDetector"[0m[39m>[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m24[0m[39m:      <detector-exclude [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mclass[0m[39m=[0m[32m"org[0m[32m.apache.tika.detect.zip.DefaultZipContainerDetector"[0m[35m/[0m[39m>[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m25[0m[39m:      <detector-exclude [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mclass[0m[39m=[0m[32m"org[0m[32m.apache.tika.detect.microsoft.POIFSContainerDetector"[0m[35m/[0m[39m>[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m26[0m[39m:    <[0m[35m/[0m[95mdetector[0m[39m>[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Core Issue Analysis[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe vulnerability in `ShellCodeDetector.java` stems from a critical logic error on [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m where the sanitized `fileName` is passed to `ProcessBuilder` as a command [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto execute, rather than executing the actual script file that was copied to [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tmpFile`. This allows an attacker to trigger execution of arbitrary system [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcommands by crafting archive entries with names matching system commands [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"ls"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"cat"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"whoami"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Root Cause:**[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Line [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m - VULNERABLE CODE[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfileName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Executes fileName as a system[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcommand[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe code copies the actual shell script content to `tmpFile` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m99[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but then [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtries to execute `fileName` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe sanitized name from metadata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m instead of the file [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat was just created. This is a fundamental misunderstanding of how [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ProcessBuilder` works.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix Implementation Strategy[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Primary Fix Location:** [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/detect/ShellCodeDetector.java` lines [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m101[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Correct the ProcessBuilder Command**[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace line [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfileName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWith:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Make the Temporary File Executable**[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter line [0m[1;36m99[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcopying the file[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mFiles.copy[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtis.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, tmpFile, StandardCopyOption.REPLACE_EXISTING[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtmpFile.toFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.setExecutable[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Make the script executable[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis ensures the script file has execute permissions before attempting to run it.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Handle Platform-Specific Execution**[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mFor better cross-platform compatibility and security, consider using an explicit [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshell interpreter. After creating `tmpFile` and making it executable, use:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mString shellPath = [0m[1;35mSystem.getProperty[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"os.name"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toLowerCase[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"win"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ? [0m[32m"cmd"[0m[39m [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    : [0m[32m"/bin/sh"[0m[39m;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mshellPath, [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHowever, for Unix/Linux systems [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich is the primary target for shell scripts[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe simpler approach of directly executing the file path is sufficient:[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Complete Patch for ShellCodeDetector.java [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m96[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m101[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPath cwd = [0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"."[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPath tmpDir = [0m[1;35mFiles.createTempDirectory[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcwd, [0m[32m"tika-shell-detect-"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPath tmpFile = [0m[1;35mtmpDir.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfileName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mFiles.copy[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtis.getPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, tmpFile, StandardCopyOption.REPLACE_EXISTING[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtmpFile.toFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.setExecutable[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m ADD THIS LINE[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mFIX THIS LINE[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mpb.directory[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtmpDir.toFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Why This is the Optimal Fix:**[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Preserves Intended Functionality:** The detector's purpose is to test if a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshell script can run without arguments. The fix maintains this by executing the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactual script file instead of a system command.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Minimal Code Changes:** Only two lines need modification [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m100[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddition [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexecutable permission[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, minimizing risk of breaking existing [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Follows Established Patterns:** The fix aligns with how `FileCommandDetector` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproperly handles file paths [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m122[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m123[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m using absolute paths and proper [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mescaping.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **No Configuration Changes Required:** The fix works within the existing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetector chain without requiring users to modify configurations.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Cross-Platform Considerations:** Using `[0m[1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprovides a platform-independent absolute path.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**How It Addresses the Vulnerability:**[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Before:** `[0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfileName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` where `fileName` could be [0m[32m"ls"[0m[39m, causing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msystem [0m[32m"ls"[0m[39m command execution[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **After:** `[0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` where the full [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath is something like `[0m[35m/tmp/tika-shell-detect-12345/[0m[95mls.sh[0m[39m`, which executes the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactual script file, not the system command[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Preserved Logic:**[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Shell script detection via extension and shebang [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m57[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m82[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains unchanged[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- File name sanitization [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m89[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m95[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains unchanged[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Temporary directory creation and cleanup [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m96[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m97[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m108[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains unchanged[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Timeout and process execution handling [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m103[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains unchanged[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Metadata setting for SHELL_NO_ARGS [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m104[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m106[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains unchanged[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: File Execute Permissions**[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Issue:** On some systems, [0m[1;35mFiles.copy[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m may not preserve executable permissions[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Mitigation:** Explicitly set executable with [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mtmpFile.toFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.setExecutable[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Shebang Requirement**[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Issue:** Direct execution requires the script to have a valid shebang [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m#![0m[35m/bin/[0m[95msh[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Mitigation:** The detector already validates shebang presence [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m71[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m74[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis is consistent[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Path Length Limits**[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Issue:** Absolute paths might be longer than relative names[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Mitigation:** Modern systems support long paths; the temporary directory path [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis deterministic and short[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Platform Differences**[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Issue:** Windows doesn't natively support shebang execution[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Mitigation:** The detector is primarily for Unix/Linux shell scripts [0m[1;39m([0m[39m.sh, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m.bash extensions[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; Windows batch files use different extensions [0m[1;39m([0m[39m.bat, .cmd[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Testing Considerations[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix should be validated with:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate shell scripts** with various filenames to ensure they execute [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Malicious filenames** matching system commands [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[32m"ls.sh"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"cat.sh"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mverify they don't trigger command injection[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Scripts with and without shebangs** to validate detection logic[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Scripts that exit with [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m** to verify SHELL_NO_ARGS metadata is set correctly[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Scripts that exit with non-zero** to verify proper handling[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Large files** to test timeout handling [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m103[0m[39m has 20s timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Alternative Approaches Considered[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Alternative [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Remove ShellCodeDetector Entirely**[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Would eliminate risk but remove functionality[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Not recommended unless the feature is deemed unnecessary[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Alternative [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Use Explicit Shell Interpreter**[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"/bin/sh"[0m[39m, [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- More explicit but adds platform dependency[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Could be added as enhancement but not required for security fix[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Alternative [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Disable by Default via Configuration**[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Requires user action and doesn't fix the underlying bug[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Only mitigates, doesn't resolve the vulnerability[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m. Similar Code Patterns[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReviewed other detectors for similar patterns:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **FileCommandDetector** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m121[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m124[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Correctly uses file path as argument to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mknown command[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No other detectors in the codebase have similar command execution vulnerabilities[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Conclusion[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix is straightforward: change line [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m to execute the absolute path of [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tmpFile` instead of the sanitized `fileName`. Add executable permission on the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile after copying. This resolves the command injection vulnerability while [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserving the detector's intended functionality of identifying no-argument shell [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscripts.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a critical security vulnerability [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOS Command Injection[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetected during fuzzing of the Apache Tika codebase. The vulnerability occurs in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ShellCodeDetector.java` when executing OS commands with attacker-controlled data. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch was attempted that modified how the command is executed by using the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mabsolute path of the temporary file instead of just the filename, and setting the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile as executable. However, after applying the patch, the same OS Command [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInjection security issue persists, indicating that the patch did not adequately [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress the root cause of the vulnerability.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzing process identified a critical security vulnerability [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical: OS Command [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInjection`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in the Apache Tika codebase. The stack trace shows the following [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexecution flow:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The fuzzer invokes `[0m[1;35mTikaAppUnpackerFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` which calls [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparseOne[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. This triggers a parsing chain through `[0m[1;35mTikaCLI.main[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` → `[0m[1;35mTikaCLI.process[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` → [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TikaCLI$[0m[1;35mOutputType.process[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The `AutoDetectParser` delegates to `CompositeParser` which handles package [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing via `PackageParser`[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. When parsing embedded documents, `[0m[1;35mFileEmbeddedDocumentExtractor.parseEmbedded[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis invoked[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. This leads to `[0m[1;35mCompositeDetector.detect[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calling `[0m[1;35mShellCodeDetector.detect[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Finally, `[0m[1;35mProcessUtils.execute[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` creates and starts a process via [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mProcessBuilder.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at line [0m[1;36m103[0m[39m of `ShellCodeDetector.java`[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe security scanner flags this as allowing execution of OS commands with [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mattacker-controlled data, which could lead to remote code execution.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch modified the `ShellCodeDetector.java` file with the following changes:[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/detect/ShellCodeDetector.java`[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes made at lines [0m[1;36m97[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m104[0m[39m:**[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m: Added `[0m[1;35mtmpFile.toFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.setExecutable[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` to explicitly set the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtemporary file as executable[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m101[0m[39m: Changed `ProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfileName[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` to [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ProcessBuilder pb = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtmpFile.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe intent of the patch appears to be:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Explicitly control the executable permission of the temporary file[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Use the absolute path of the temporary file instead of just the filename when [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructing the ProcessBuilder[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Result[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the same OS Command Injection security issue is still [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetected with an identical stack trace, except:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The line number in `[0m[1;35mShellCodeDetector.detect[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` changed from line [0m[1;36m103[0m[39m to line [0m[1;36m104[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mdue to the added line[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
